The healthy kids are
the ones who are not

00:13:16.490 --> 00:13:18.110 align:middle line:90%
eating all the processed foods.

00:13:18.110 --> 00:13:20.240 align:middle line:10%
They're eating more
whole foods diet

00:13:20.240 --> 00:13:23.270 align:middle line:10%
